<br>
Right before you spawn the first 2 all the tanks sit down in the corner kil was talking about...and all the casters stand at the bottum of the steps....this causes the giants to go right after teh melee and leave the casters alone....<br>
<br>
Make sure you kill Gorgon first.....that way the 3rd doesnt spawn with 1 still left....then right before the 2nd one dies all casters stand and as soon as it dies all melee sit...repeat till none left....this makes it go super fast do to no ping pong at all...<br>
<br>
<br>
One other trick that some learn hardway is when it rampages only MA keeps attacking all other stop until it is done..<br>
